00Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主坐好耐定la<br />\n國文教育個時已經係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔介意坐得耐，<br />\n我介意冇人宣揚出去，香港就沒有然後了"},{"pid":"e7a1a75c39f7cffb07a95b84049e833479e7e152","tid":450154,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:26:49.000Z","msg":"呢個就over咗<br />\n佢出流行經典50年已經算係咁"},{"pid":"318a724c1902ad7590e5e7a5560f9bbc487ab890","tid":450154,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T23:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個就over咗<br />\n佢出流行經典50年已經算係咁</blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n成日屈得就屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87957298ba5e68eca545eab0087d87bba586d5e8","tid":450154,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個就over咗<br />\n佢出流行經典50年已經算係咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b407ac4e86cd23112dfc89adc23ecb348990d9c","tid":450154,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T03:35:35.000Z","msg":"Pishhhh"},{"pid":"d5b01a5fe925055c6bc197d2c94e72155374ea60","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:45:52.000Z","msg":"溫水煮港豬"},{"pid":"91584a7b718189f154bcbe67f1c73401d6f35658","tid":450154,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T04:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f50eaf14c02a5262b004c11b4ae7e7dbab91c93e","tid":450154,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會去香港本地文化的，一國兩制和基本法講左在不抵觸基本法的原則下，保留香港固有生活方式和制度。大陸要藉著落實一國兩制和基本法話俾地球人聽，中國的innovative政策，講得出做得到，建立下國際型象。今期施政報告講的大灣區、一帶一路、港豬澳、一地兩檢，全部都要同大陸結合。有些香港人敵視大陸，有些就唔太知道大陸的實際情況，對大陸冇信心，這些情況都不利以上結合projects。要改善這些情況，就要在香港宣傳多點大陸，硬如反調強調國家觀念，軟如電視節目，都是想令香港人認同大陸。得到人民認同，政策才順利推行，健康發展。近排好興講可持續發展，可持續的意思是長命，如果不健康，怎樣長命呢？</blockquote><br />\n三個官方聲明收你皮:<br />\n歷史文件<br />\n兩制係過程, 一國係目的<br />\n全面管制<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c2c0c8590d3ee7c6cf292eacd55636a602f9bbb7","tid":450154,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T07:13:16.000Z","msg":"推一推，好多5毛洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd318060332962a7e6c9ccfb849fa44bb3317d2a","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T07:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"670d4458ddb778ff088c556a6706d276b4f40845","tid":450154,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本香港人自己不思進取，食老本，另一方面又唔重視自己文化，一味金錢至上，唔好怪人地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一個地方既人民係咩人，係由當地政府有心營造出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n政府提供一個環境姐，最緊要係d人，香港一直比人屌文化沙漠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解美英歐國會係大多數人想去既地方？算唔算答左你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為歐美國家係資本主義下，最先獲得物質文明既國家，佢地向世界輸出物質文明。而大部份人都被洗腦。<br />\n<br />\n大多數人﹖問左伊斯蘭既人，用另一套文化去睇既人先唔該"},{"pid":"f9e90760630dd9fd5d22d23a26c4c8f5ef2ea20e","tid":450154,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家講緊文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 歐美本身d人重視文化，有文化素養；但香港人搵錢至上，攪文化都只係為搵錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n為錢都好過唔攪丫，咪當係一個起步囉。歐美社會，較香港他條，節奏慢得多，咪有時間欣賞下文化藝術之美，洗滌心靈囉。其實我覺得香港有些文化好正㗎。例如，起到d樓又高又密，遠望好似一堆長條積木。夜晚放工，勁多車，塞住晒，但望出去，汽車的燈佈滿回旋處、天穚、道路，幾靚的。有些區混混亂咁，人多車多招牌多噪音多，在呢個極易誘發精神病的環境中，不少店鋪、街霸好有秩序地做小生意。香港地，環境又夠多樣化，想體驗水貨客就去水水屯門，想體驗混亂就去旺角，想體驗印度人南亞人就去尖咀深水埗，想體驗西方感就去老蘭，想體驗大自然就大把山行。嘢食又大把選擇，雖然味道有待改進，但至少大把得揀囉，外國好多品牌來插旗嘛。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有無諗過歐美社會一個做勞當奴既人。佢工人高過印度人做勞當幾倍到十倍。係點解﹖<br />\n<br />\n點解歐美人佢地可以「他條，節奏慢」﹖"},{"pid":"ad5dd77eefbc667dde3ee94a68dd5e4948b0dc39","tid":450154,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"其實好明顯, 拆天星碼頭, 普教中, 強制輸入蝗, CCTVB播支那劇, 多到數唔晒"},{"pid":"c5100f702e400b3507295ad80e58d106cecbe3ec","tid":450154,"uid":20000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:06:32.000Z","msg":"你終於訓醒啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b7d125dcffe53303f6e429874badbff1a9cc31","tid":450154,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"對香港人好重要的貼！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但不多人跟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485e152af221b20ee39e42d81a8d8492595c2878","tid":450154,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"樓主坐咗監十幾廿年？"},{"pid":"8f7bce8536a69cbb6fb5e1fad9b100bdc907e5b0","tid":450154,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T14:53:49.000Z","msg":"小學已經加大緊力度種族清洗"},{"pid":"f35ca26eedc9b0583b1cb9444fa3cbf8e9364ace","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T15:04:10.000Z","msg":"贊同"},{"pid":"ca839e10ac42649d5b6608bd75735a3c9ad4aaaf","tid":450154,"uid":9398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T17:11:26.000Z","msg":"頂番上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b1c84f11f68d7fc693f535d03cf5824c41b856","tid":450154,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"早廿年前已經係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a704c2d8bafbb6d597a324e4050d3a9852c0f36f","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"23b37b59fa4c52929733f39013b2fa7dbd57732a","tid":450154,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"睇新疆，蒙古就知啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們的香港都畀共產黨滅緊文化！"},{"pid":"77363c322f19236d10b72a349dba4a84291b848e","tid":450154,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教育政策真係最難攪<br />\n係條街聽到有學生講普通話就嬲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明著住香港的學校校服，居然講北方契丹人嘅「胡語」，不論不類！"},{"pid":"2a544a19e0d59b9b243a3fb57e1a99345c39ea05","tid":450154,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b7950bbc9a2a9774a2bc6d6786b195f6dd57da","tid":450154,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:12:42.000Z","msg":"好多五毛，請善用起底功能或睇五毛List"},{"pid":"3faab077f512341a54c30b051c5398652fb82762","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ffa98afce5ec26aef56cb29a6201cd4ee6d0cd","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5620f5ec6e2cd9c9af9e57b928e572c7a3215803","tid":450154,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:27.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"55dc8bb4431157c143a92a8f1a2787456529aae8","tid":450154,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱啱赤柱出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔出奇<br />\n岩岩有人仲講返「14億人賺14億」黎串我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /